  "title": "Fast Barter",
  "description": "Instant piglin bartering for faster trades!",
  "body": "<!-- Banner -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XDN2rOo.png\" alt=\"Fast Barter Banner\" width=\"100%\">\n</p>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Title -->\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"6\">\n      <strong>Fast Barter</strong>\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Short Description -->\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"5\">\n      Fast Barter is a lightweight Minecraft datapack that makes piglin bartering instant.\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Badges -->\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/yXBpHEg7GE\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img alt=\"Discord\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1404839869632745542?style=flat-square&logo=discord&label=Join%20Server\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/forgedmc/fast-barter\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img alt=\"GitHub\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/View%20Source-Github-white?style=flat-square&logo=github\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Description -->\n<p>\n  <span>\n    <strong>Fast Barter</strong> removes the waiting time from piglin bartering, allowing trades to happen instantly\n    after a piglin receives gold. It keeps the vanilla bartering system intact while making large-scale trading\n    faster, cleaner, and less frustrating.\n  </span>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n  <span>\n    Whether you are speedrunning, farming resources, or improving a survival server, <strong>Fast Barter</strong>\n    gives piglin trading a sharper pace without changing the core Minecraft experience.\n  </span>\n</p>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Divider -->\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://placehold.co/838x4/c13b3d/ffffff?text=%E2%80%8B\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"838\" height=\"4\">\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Installation -->\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"5\">\n      <strong>Installation</strong>\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span>Download the latest version of <strong>Fast Barter</strong>.</span></li>\n  <li><span>Place the datapack inside your world’s <code>datapacks</code> folder.</span></li>\n  <li><span>Open the world and run <code>/reload</code>.</span></li>\n  <li><span>Use <code>/datapack list</code> to confirm it is enabled.</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>\n  <span>\n    After installation, piglin bartering will work instantly. No setup command is required.\n  </span>\n</p>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Divider -->\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://placehold.co/838x4/c13b3d/ffffff?text=%E2%80%8B\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"838\" height=\"4\">\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- In-Game Preview -->\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"5\">\n      <strong>Instant Piglin Bartering</strong>\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dsAzxal.gif\" alt=\"Fast Barter In-Game Preview\" width=\"951\">\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<p>\n  <span>\n    Piglins no longer hold onto gold before giving loot. With <strong>Fast Barter</strong>, trades resolve instantly,\n    making bartering farms significantly faster and more responsive.\n  </span>\n</p>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Divider -->\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://placehold.co/838x4/c13b3d/ffffff?text=%E2%80%8B\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"838\" height=\"4\">\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Uninstall -->\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"5\">\n      <strong>Uninstalling</strong>\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<p>\n  <span>\n    To safely remove <strong>Fast Barter</strong>, run:\n  </span>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n  <code>/function fast_barter:cmd/uninstall</code>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n  <span>\n    Then remove the datapack from your world’s <code>datapacks</code> folder.\n  </span>\n</p>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- Divider -->\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://placehold.co/838x4/c13b3d/ffffff?text=%E2%80%8B\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"838\" height=\"4\">\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<!-- License -->\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"4\">\n      <strong><em>License:</em></strong>\n      <em>\n        This datapack is released under the\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/ForgedMC/.github/blob/main/LICENSE\" target=\"_blank\">Forged License</a>.\n      </em>\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n<br />\n\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <font size=\"4\">\n      <strong><em>Fast Barter is a ForgedMC datapack.</em></strong>\n    </font>\n  </span>\n</center>",
